  {"t":"tip","head":"Best time to visit","html":"April–June and September–October hit the sweet spot: warm enough for the coast and day trips, markets in full swing, without August's peak heat and cruise crowds. Summer still works for a nightlife-focused trip, since the center stays lively late into the night — just note that some family-run places on our eats list close one day a week or take a summer break, so check before a special trip."},
