    "<strong>Pani ca meusa</strong> — the spleen sandwich: boiled-then-fried veal spleen and lung in a soft vastedda roll, served 'schettu' (plain, with lemon) or 'maritata' (with ricotta and caciocavallo). Look for the steel steam-carts around Vucciria and Ballarò.",
